      "text": "• Put out 9 counters.\n• Pick a number card and add that many\ncounters.\n\n• Write an equation to represent the counters.\nCan you write more than 1?\n\nEquations:\n\nRound 1:\n\nRound 2:\n\nRound 3:\n\nRound 4:\n\nRound 5:"
