      "heading": "Activity 2 — Student Task Statement",
      "line": 266,
      "source_guide": "curriculum/im_teacher_guides/grade1/unit3/lesson17.md",
      "text": "1. Clare draws some birds.\nShe draws 3 birds in a nest and 9 birds flying.\nHow many birds did she draw?\nShow your thinking using drawings, numbers,\nor words.\n\n2. Clare draws birds that like warm weather.\nShe draws 6 toucans and 8 parrots.\nHow many birds did she draw?\n\nShow your thinking using drawings, numbers,\nor words.\n\n3. Clare draws birds that like cold weather.\n\nShe draws 7 penguins and 5 owls.\nHow many birds did she draw?\nShow your thinking using drawings, numbers,\nor words."
    },
